@timestamp = {{$timestamp}}

### 打开 SSE 连接（Express，端口 3000）
GET http://localhost:3000/sse?userId=alice
Accept: text/event-stream

### 向 alice 发送定向通知
POST http://localhost:3000/notify/alice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "msg": "hi alice (express)",
  "time": "{{timestamp}}"
}

### 全员广播（跨实例需配置 Redis 并使用 publish）
POST http://localhost:3000/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "msg": "broadcast from express",
  "time": "{{timestamp}}"
}

### 向房间 global 发送（同实例）
POST http://localhost:3000/room/global
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "msg": "room message (express)",
  "time": "{{timestamp}}"
}

### 发布到房间 global（如配置 Redis，可跨实例）
POST http://localhost:3000/publish-room/global
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "msg": "published room message (express)",
  "time": "{{timestamp}}"
}

### 关闭 alice 的所有连接（演示）
POST http://localhost:3000/close/alice
Content-Type: application/json

{}
